{
    "story_id": "",
    "story_icon": "",
    "outline": {
        "title": "",
        "content": [
            "要跳过此剧情吗？"
        ]
    },
    "story_content": [
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "抱歉，尤蒂尔。\\n可以过来一下吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "怎么了？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "啊，那个……该怎么说。\\n好啦，你来了就知道了。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "…… \\n兰扎卜这家伙，到底怎么了？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "所以说，我不能\\n让你这样的人进入城堡。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110041_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "天音",
            "context": "为什么……为什么要藏匿龙！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110041_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "天音",
            "context": "那是灾厄！\\n是应该毁灭的存在啊！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "就算你这么说……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "怎么了，库菈乌？\\n这女孩是？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "啊，尤蒂尔。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "她一直坚持\\n要见碧龙……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110041_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "天音",
            "context": "你就是跟龙缔结契约的\\n尤蒂尔对吧？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110041_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "天音",
            "context": "我名为天音！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110041_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "天音",
            "context": "是以“没有龙的世界”为目标的\\n奇迹之神子！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "我听说过。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "在以龙的灭绝为目标的小国，\\n有一位被称作“奇迹之神子”的人。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "那位神子，似乎是过去被龙毁灭的村落里\\n唯一的生还者。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "所以才叫奇迹之神子吗……\\n这么小的孩子……真是不可思议。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110041_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "天音",
            "context": "什么！？别把我当小孩子！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110041_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "天音",
            "context": "我已经24岁。\\n是个如假包换的大人了！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "咦？是、是吗……\\n那真是抱歉……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110041_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "天音",
            "context": "知道就好！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110041_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "天音",
            "context": "呃……所以刚才是在说……\\n啊，对、对了！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110041_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "天音",
            "context": "龙凭借强大的力量屠杀人类，\\n是会招来不幸、如灾厄般的存在。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110041_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "天音",
            "context": "所以我想要在这座\\n有龙居住的城堡，\\n寻找那些家伙的弱点！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "喔。那你去找其他人吧。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "知道这种理由后，\\n怎么可能乖乖放你进入城堡啊。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110041_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "天音",
            "context": "唔……\\n你们果然要保护龙吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110041_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "天音",
            "context": "但是，我不会就此作罢！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110041_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "天音",
            "context": "我要一直在这里坐着，\\n直到你们打开大门为止！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "恕我直言，在这里坐上好多天，\\n真的没问题吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "还是在造成骚动前先回去……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110041_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "天音",
            "context": "找出龙的弱点才是最重要的！\\n那正是我们的宿愿！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110041_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "天音",
            "context": "所以没问题……大概吧！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "唉……事情变得棘手了。\\n怎么办呢，尤蒂尔。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "我明白了……既然你都那么说了，\\n好吧，那就进来吧。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "喂、喂喂……这样可以吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "要是耶梦加得\\n发生什么事的话……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "的确，或许龙有着像她所说的\\n如灾厄般的一面。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "但是，\\n也有像耶梦加得那样的存在。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "只要真正相处过，她就会了解，\\n世上也有善良的龙。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "而且凭我的直觉，\\n她是个很直率的人吧？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "我觉得只要好好谈，大家就能互相理解。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "虽然我很担心……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "但既然是尤蒂尔的决定，\\n我会照办的。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "走吧，天音。我带你参观城堡，\\n跟我来。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110041_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "天音",
            "context": "啊，这一刻终于到来了！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110041_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "天音",
            "context": "我要实现\\n没有龙存在的世界！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        }
    ]
}